Text: The only way to protect what's yours...

As Gettan swings his sword, a sudden blow sends him
reeling.
Yukime feels a presence nearby and shifts her gaze.
Like a lamb to the slaughter...
Gettan's unseeing eyes glare at John Smith.
John Smith swiftly closes in on Gettan.
...to take back something very important you stole!
So, you're the one who stole from me.
It's you who stole from me!

I'm only here to take back something very important
you stole.
Typical of a lowlife to play dumb, John Smith!
Something important to you... You're a kind person...
I believe you have something to tell me...!

Hungry for more power, Gettan moves to consume
a red pill.
I believe you have something to tell me.
I believe you have something to tell me.
What you have to tell me.

Gettan looks up at John Smith, various emotions
running across his face.
You can leave it to me.

John Smith runs magic through his hands,
then strokes Yukime's wound.

(I think he said it was buried under the "yew" over
there or something, right...?)
I've got one last job I need to do.
